column1098:
Dear {{ resume_screening_data.candidate_name }},



Thank you for your interest in the {{ resume_screening_data.position_applied }} position in our {{ resume_screening_data.department }} department.



We have reviewed your resume and would like to schedule a phone screening interview.



The phone interview will take approximately 30-45 minutes and will cover:
• Your background and experience
• Interest in the role and company
• Basic qualification verification
• Role expectations and next steps



Please reply with your availability for the next 3-5 business days, and we will schedule the call.



Best regards,
HR Team
column1099:
Dear {{ resume-screening_data.candidate_name }},

Thank you for your interest in the {{ resume-screening_data.position_applied }} position at our company.

After careful review of your application, we have decided to move forward with other candidates whose experience more closely matches our current requirements.

We appreciate the time you took to apply and encourage you to apply for future opportunities that match your background.

Best regards,
HR Team
column1100:
Dear {{ resume-screening_data.candidate_name }},

Congratulations! You have successfully passed our phone screening for the {{ resume-screening_data.position_applied }} position.

Next Step: Skills Assessment

You will receive an assessment relevant to your role that should take approximately 2-3 hours to complete. The assessment will evaluate:
• Role-specific technical or functional skills
• Problem-solving abilities
• Practical application of knowledge
• Best practices in your field

Please complete the assessment within 48 hours of receiving it. You may use standard resources you would typically use in your work.

We will send the assessment details shortly.

Best regards,
{{ resume-screening_data.department }} Team
column1101:
Dear {{ resume-screening_data.candidate_name }},

Thank you for taking the time to speak with us during your phone interview for the {{ resume-screening_data.position_applied }} position.

After careful consideration, we have decided to move forward with other candidates whose experience and background more closely align with our current needs.

We were impressed with your interest in our company and encourage you to apply for future opportunities that may be a better fit.

Thank you again for your time and interest.

Best regards,
HR Team
column1102:

Congratulations! You have successfully passed our skills assessment with a score of {{ assessment_eval.assessment_score }}/10.

• Format: Video call or in-person (details to follow)

  - Role-specific discussion and scenarios

Please reply with your availability for the next 5-7 business days.

Best regards,
{{ resume-screening_data.department }} Team

column1104:

• Interviewers: Senior team members and/or department head
• Focus Areas:
  - Advanced role-specific discussions
  - Leadership and growth potential
  - Strategic thinking and decision-making
  - Final cultural fit assessment
  - Meet potential team members

Best regards,
{{ resume-screening_data.department }} Team
